<br>
No life, friends, phone calls ever at all? You can be a main tank or a main cleric!! We require your constant attention for success so you wont have time to think about your lonely worthless existence as you make sure the mobs stay off the guild or you make sure the guild stays in the red.<br>
<br>
Do you generally just want to seem important while you chat in 15 channels or cyber your online BF/GF? We have many choices!! Be a ranger...when not eating a death touch or harmshield pulling some insane boss into place, you can cheerfully send huggles and kisses out to all your friends while you wait for your 15th rezz. Or be a shaman, just pre slow and debuff that thing then when it kils you its all your time while the guild kills it for phat lewts!!<br>
<br>
Or maybe you cant sit still, be a rogue shadowknight or monk.  You can spend all your time running ahead and pulling trains on the group so you dont get too bored.<br>
